summary:
STANDALONE and MARRIAGABLE followers.

Two Version of an Elf follower and one totally revised and new! Totally Standalone, you would just need SKSE.
descriptionHtml:
So there's two Yjorld this time because I noticed you kinda liked it :


- the old Yjorld who is already a good mage but retired from the Winterhold Academy you will find her at the Drunken Huntsman in Whiterun.

- The apprentice Yjorld ( From the past) who is a Winterhold student, you will find her at the archives in the Winterholm Academy
